I am creating custom macros that require getting information associated to a JIRA project. For this, the user needs to select the JIRA Project. 

Please create a new macro parameter option type of "jiraproject" that displays an autocomplete field for searching JIRA projects.

For this scenario, the user would need to select the server first. Therefore, CONF-37572 would be handy.

