I see CONF-28154 converts confluence links automatically when I paste in a URL to confluence itself. However, many of our users are not aware of this functionality. Also, the fact that when a user clicks the {{Link}} button it usually brings up the {{Web Link}} dialog, users are initially led to use the full URL to a Confluence page. 

Please display a warning on the {{Web Link}} page when a user is pasting in a Confluence link and also provide a button that they can click which will convert that web link to a Wiki link. 

Please make this work for both full Link URL as well as the Tiny Link URL.

